FT  01 FEB 94 / People: Safeway Stores
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Roger Partington, formerly UK marketing director of Nestle, has been
appointed marketing director of SAFEWAY STORES.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>Safeway Stores.
</CO>
<XX>
