The 1994 summer festival opens on May 28th with a performance of Mozart's Le
nozze di Figaro. The top seat price has been raised from Pounds 90 to Pounds
100 this season but for the first time there will be seats at Pounds 30 and
Pounds 15, plus the introduction of 42 standing places at Pounds 10 each,
sold on the day of the performance. It is expected that the seats available
to the general public will rise to almost 25 per cent of capacity.
