FT  31 JAN 94 / Observer: No show Willie
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Five months after moving to London on the Bank of England's insistence
following HSBC's takeover of Midland, Sir William Purves is hardly a
familiar part of the City scenery. But his determination to maintain a low
profile reaches new heights this month. He is not going to turn up to his
