Mackenzie in the Granada camp these days by virtue of his new job managing
British Sky Broadcasting, partly-owned by Granada?
Granada insists that the 10 facts about LWT were all its own work and not a
straight lift from The Sun's editorial style book. Fortunately for LWT,
Granada's knocking copy is bound by the rules of the Takeover Panel rather
